{"tid":219670,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃洋達：同毓民嘅人打邊爐就係匪！","createTime":"2017-04-27T11:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T10:51:58.000Z","uid":91432,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2307b497a753ed09dbd529df1835c6f3e09876b7","tid":219670,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"（前熱血骨幹）Cat Cat Leung<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=362523850808345&amp;set=a.247851515608913.1073741830.100011521983645&amp;type=3&amp;hc_location=ufi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D362523850808345%26set%3Da.247851515608913.1073741830.100011521983645%26type%3D3%26hc_location%3Dufi&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGEwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=717841c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=362523850808345&amp;set=a.247851515608913.1073741830.100011521983645&amp;type=3&amp;hc_location=ufi</a><br />\n<br />\n22 April &middot;<br />\n <br />\n今年年初時,毓民司機Jim Lai約咗法國佬<code>李政熙兄弟</code>我及其餘幾個frd去佢家BBQ,光頭達收到消息後,就在熱時編採組秘密群組內說 : Cat姐<code>法國佬</code>李政熙`李珏熙都係匪,去呢個BBQ嘅就係通匪,就係與我為敵 !<br />\n<br />\n下圖係光頭撚達叫個臭閪老婆確認Jim Lai係通匪,及臭閪嘅回應 !<br />\n<br />\n屌你地兩公婆十八代老母臭閪 !!!<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Jim Lai係毓民嘅人,Jim Lai通匪,係咪毓民都通匪呀???</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你地兩公婆十八代老母臭閪 !!!<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>毓民同我好frd㗎 ! 係咪毓民都通匪呀???</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你隻臭閪咁撚有型牙? 可以確認邊個係匪牙??? 你兩條仆街仲惡撚過共產黨wor&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n既然咁撚勁就咪撚鳩縮喇屌你地老母臭化閪 !!!"},{"pid":"3bb0080f8a5b444e74b13fb769f44e9cd46eada2","tid":219670,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75652523c4b6715f5e1d5d255a54464343fe6da2","tid":219670,"uid":82500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:27:25.000Z","msg":"屌你、BBQ係燒嘢食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal